Package jade.util

Class Summary
BidirectionalMap<K,V> A bidirectial map is a map that supports look of values via keys, as well as keys via value.
ColoredChar Represents a char with an associated color.
Coord Represents an integer cartesian coordinate.
Dice Dice basically extends Random and adds a few methods.
Multimap<K,V> A multimap is a map in which more than one value may be associated with and returned for a given key.
Tools Tools contains lots of methods that are generally useful, but do not fit in any one jade class.
